translated: Leijonhufvud, Sten Knut Arthur C :-son, Baron, Norrköping, b. 19/5/16 in Stockholm, son of Baron Carl S. L. and Margit Frestadius. Married in 1941 to Märtha Mathilde Madeleine Koskull. - Completed high school in Strängnäs in 1936, obtained a law degree in 1942. Served as a judicial clerk in Bråbygdens and Finspångaläns district court in Norrköping from 1942 to 1945, employed by the local tax board in Norrköping since 1945. Hobbies: hunting and sport fishing.
